insert into "books" ("description", "image_url", "title") values ('Robust Control Design with MATLAB¬Æ (second edition) helps the student to learn how to use well-developed advanced robust control design methods in practical cases. To this end, several realistic control design examples from teaching-laboratory experiments, such as a two-wheeled, self-balancing robot, to complex systems like a flexible-link manipulator are given detailed presentation. All of these exercises are conducted using MATLAB¬Æ Robust Control Toolbox 3, Control System Toolbox and Simulink¬Æ. By sharing their experiences in industrial cases with minimum recourse to complicated theories and formulae, the authors convey essential ideas and useful insights into robust industrial control systems design using major H-infinity optimization and related methods allowing readers quickly to move on with their own challenges. The hands-on tutorial style of this text rests on an abundance of examples and features for the second edition: ‚Ä¢ rewritten and simplified presentation of theoretical and methodological material including original coverage of linear matrix inequalities; ‚Ä¢ new Part II forming a tutorial on Robust Control Toolbox 3; ‚Ä¢ fresh design problems including the control of a two-rotor dynamic system; and ‚Ä¢ end-of-chapter exercises. Electronic supplements to the written text that can be downloaded from extras.springer.com/isbn include: ‚Ä¢ M-files developed with MATLAB¬Æ help in understanding the essence of robust control system design portrayed in text-based examples; ‚Ä¢ MDL-files for simulation of open- and closed-loop systems in Simulink¬Æ; and ‚Ä¢ a solutions manual available free of charge to those adopting Robust Control Design with MATLAB¬Æ as a textbook for courses. Robust Control Design with MATLAB¬Æ is for graduate students and practising engineers who want to learn how to deal with robust control design problems without spending a lot of time in researching complex theoretical developments.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=J9C4BAAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Robust Control Design with MATLAB¬Æ');
